rientation: landscape)" srcset="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0079/3287/0756/t/6/assets/pf-27a1939c--dosageofmeloxicamfordogssideeffects_400x181.jpg?v=1595692363&resized 1x, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0079/3287/0756/t/6/assets/pf-27a1939c--dosageofmeloxicamfordogssideeffects.jpg?v=1595692363 2x"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0079/3287/0756/t/6/assets/pf-27a1939c--dosageofmeloxicamfordogssideeffects.jpg?v=1595692363" alt="dosage-of-meloxicam-for-dogs-side-effects" title="dosage-of-meloxicam-for-dogs-side-effects"></picture></div></div></div><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-1b98c308 pf-r pf-r-eh" data-pf-type="Row" style="--pf-s-lg:15px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--undefined"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-36a5fd56" data-pf-type="Column"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-0836a5fd"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-f60836a5"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-17500e06"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-daf60836">Just like humans, senior dogs are prone to Osteoarthritis. Unfortunately, you cannot cure Osteoarthritis. As a responsible and caring dog owner, it is natural for you to want to improve your dog's quality of life, at least.
<br>
<br>Meloxicam (also referred to as Metacam) can ease your dog's discomfort and can improve quality of life, but there are some potentially severe side effects. To learn more about Meloxicam and how it may help your dog, read on below.
<br></span></p></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-565244e8" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-7134aad8"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-fd565244">Table Of Contents</span></h3></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-929f04e4" data-pf-type="Column"><ul data-pf-type="List" class="sc-pcLhl bMMcvF pf-25bb4f1b" style="--text-indent:0; --line-spacing:1px;"><li data-to-section="pf-c403d2e0" href="#" data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-e8b00629 animate-backward animate-backward"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-44e8b006">What is Meloxicam?<br></span></li><li data-to-section="pf-afbb834a" href="#" data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-29faf083 animate-backward animate-backward"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-0629faf0">What is Meloxicam used for in dogs?<br></span></li><li data-to-section="pf-55bafaba" href="#" data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-839d4b45 animate-backward animate-backward"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-f0839d4b">Is Meloxicam Safe for Dogs?<br></span></li><li data-to-section="pf-4bab3f42" href="#" data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-456ca206 animate-backward animate-backward"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-4b456ca2">Meloxicam Dosage for Dogs<br></span></li><li data-to-section="pf-23aa02c8" href="#" data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-06fa1905 animate-backward animate-backward"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-a206fa19">How Much Does Meloxicam Cost?<br></span></li><li data-to-section="pf-228a2e0d" href="#" data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-05ba8281 animate-backward animate-backward"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-1905ba82">Side Effects of Meloxicam</span></li><li data-to-section="pf-a3ae7c5a" href="#" data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-81929f04 animate-backward animate-backward"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-8281929f">Natural Alternatives</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="sc-pZopv bjKdkd pf-7f79ed35" id="sticky-01" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-pQQXS iWCqut" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-7f257f79 pf-r pf-r-eh" data-pf-type="Row" style="--pf-s-lg:15px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--3 pf-c-md--3 pf-c-lg--3"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-e587ec8d" data-pf-type="Column"></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--3 pf-c-md--3 pf-c-lg--3"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-ec8dfbf0" data-pf-type="Column"></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--3 pf-c-md--3 pf-c-lg--3"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-fbf01f63" data-pf-type="Column"></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--3 pf-c-md--3 pf-c-lg--3"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-1f637f25" data-pf-type="Column"><img sizes="(min-width: 992px) 1200px, (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 991px) 800px, 400px" srcset="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0079/3287/0756/t/6/assets/pf-e13b79b7--160x6002.jpg?v=1583947785 1200w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0079/3287/0756/t/6/assets/pf-e13b79b7--160x6002.jpg?v=1583947785 800w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0079/3287/0756/t/6/assets/pf-e13b79b7--160x6002_400x1500.jpg?v=1583947785&resized 400w" class="sc-qZtVr dLIPjF pf-ed35eb1d" id="" data-pf-type="Image2"></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="sc-pZopv bjKdkd pf-978456e4" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-pQQXS iWCqut" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-d9279784 pf-r pf-r-eh" data-pf-type="Row" style="--pf-s-lg:15px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--undefined"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-5ca205ae" data-pf-type="Column"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-3c63cc77"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-04e47e7e">What is Meloxicam?<br></span></h2><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-8f5ca205"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-7e8f5ca2"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-321e2611"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-7e7e8f5c">Meloxicam, also known by the brand name Metacam, is a medication used to treat inflammation and pain in dogs who suffer from Osteoarthritis. If you are familiar with Mobic, Metacam is the dog version of that.
<br>
<br>The FDA approved the use of Meloxicam for dogs as long as a veterinarian prescribes it.&nbsp;<br></span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="sc-pZopv bjKdkd pf-061ce5f4" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-pQQXS iWCqut" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-e813061c pf-r pf-r-eh" data-pf-type="Row" style="--pf-s-lg:15px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--undefined"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-aaa6f5c3" data-pf-type="Column"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-0a290d33"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-05ae99aa">What is Meloxicam used for in dogs?<br></span></h2><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-097634e8"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-99aaa6f5">Vets most commonly prescribe Meloxicam as a treatment for dogs with inflammation, stiffness, and pain caused by Osteoarthritis. However, Meloxicam can also treat symptoms of other bone and muscle disorders.
<br>
<br>Meloxicam works by reducing the hormones in your dog's body that cause inflammation and pain. It does this without the use of steroids.
<br>
<br>Additionally, vets prescribe Meloxicam to reduce pain in dogs caused by surgery or a recent injury. The drug is known to be useful for treating both chronic and short-term conditions.
<br></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="sc-pZopv bjKdkd pf-d9867fe8" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-pQQXS iWCqut" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-6aa4cc0b pf-r pf-r-eh" data-pf-type="Row" style="--pf-s-lg:15px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-90d9867f" data-pf-type="Column"><div data-pf-type="Form2" class="sc-qQAox csiTZj pf-b033da6a">{% form 'customer' %}<div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-2d90d986 pf-r pf-r-eh" data-pf-type="Row" style="--pf-s-lg:10px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-c39e562d" data-pf-type="Column"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-78904321"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-f5c39e56"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Learn about natural pet health, and be the first to know about sales and new products.
